  "texts": [
    "The histograms for each level are concatenated into a single feature vector which is used with a 1-NN classifier.",
    "While more accurate than BOSS, the increase in parameter search space and bag size makes it very difficult to run in practice.",
    "The Temporal Dictionary Ensemble (TDE) (Middlehurst et al. 2020b) combines the best improvements introduced in WEASEL, SpatialBOSS and cBOSS and also includes several novel features.",
    "TDE is an ensemble of 1-NN classifiers which transforms each series into a histogram of word counts using SFA (Schäfer and Högqvist 2012).",
    "From WEASEL, TDE takes the method for finding supervised breakpoints for discretisation, and captures frequencies of bigrams found from non-overlapping windows."
  ],
